WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.455
Today we will learn how to

00:00:02.455 --> 00:00:05.322
transplant seedlings into bigger pots. First,

00:00:05.322 --> 00:00:07.252
fill the new pot with soil.

00:00:07.252 --> 00:00:09.182
Then make a small hole in

00:00:09.182 --> 00:00:11.665
the middle. Gently place the seedling

00:00:11.665 --> 00:00:13.675
in the hole and press the

00:00:13.675 --> 00:00:15.350
soil around it. Well done!
